A couple of weeks ago I was talking to my dad about how I wanted to go look at broncos I have literally been obsessed lol, the next day we go up to Ford to test drive it, not thinking anything about getting it we go inside to talk to the people just to see because in my mind I thought there is no way this is IMPOSSIBLE 

But today I can say I’m the owner of a New Ford Bronco…. 

And I wanted to share this story because we all have dreams and things we want to accomplish that may seem IMPOSSIBLE but my God says “oh you think thats impossible, well watch this” and watch how he will open up the heavens for his sons and daughters so be encouraged the best is yet to come❤️

“i will lift my eyes unto the hills, from where does my help come? my help comes from the lord, who made heaven and earth”

(alone, sad, anxious, worried, forgotten, unworthy, not good enough, struggled financially, just lost) 

he’s always kept me and going into this new year all those same feeling will try to make its way back but it won’t prosper!! We going to the moon this year 🚀 🔥 #2023
